### BACKWARD COMPATIBILITY (api/todos)
### ===========================================

### Get all todos (default version - backward compatibility)
GET {{Todo.API_HostAddress}}/api/todos
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new todo (default version)
POST {{Todo.API_HostAddress}}/api/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Todo from HTTP Client (default version)"
}

###

