### V2 ENDPOINTS (api/v2/todos)
### ===========================================

### Get all todos (v2 - with enhanced metadata)
GET {{Todo.API_HostAddress}}/api/v2/todos
Accept: application/json

###

### Get todo by ID (v2 - with enhanced response)
GET {{Todo.API_HostAddress}}/api/v2/todos/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new todo (v2 - with enhanced validation)
POST {{Todo.API_HostAddress}}/api/v2/todos
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Todo from HTTP Client v2"
}

###

